title: Metro Lines - DC Only, Washington DC, 2002
name: Metro Lines - DC Only, Washington DC, 2002
description:
Metro Lines (regional). The dataset contains locations and attributes of Metro lines, created as part of the DC Geographic Information System (DC GIS) for the D.C. Office of the Chief Technology Officer (OCTO) by participating D.C. government agencies.

Lines were taken from legacy data from WMATA and fit to orthophotography and extracted planimetric data.
